  "detailed_description": "Embark on an exciting pixelated adventure with \"Puma: The Cat,\" a 2D platform game brimming with emotion and friendship. Take control of Puma, a lovely cat who lived happily in an animal shelter alongside her inseparable friend Mia. However, life plays a trick, and Mia is adopted by a family, leaving Puma alone.<br><br>Puma's journey to reunite with Mia is filled with challenges and dangers. In this game, you will explore a variety of maps, each with its secrets and unique challenges, while facing countless enemies and obstacles.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pixel Art Style: Enjoy the nostalgic aesthetics of pixel art, full of charm and detail.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/a771787d57b31aee70f661eb5bfec3f1.poster.avif?t=1699477566\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/a771787d57b31aee70f661eb5bfec3f1.webm?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/a771787d57b31aee70f661eb5bfec3f1.mp4?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Platforming Mechanics: Overcome clever obstacles and execute precise jumps in immersive platform gameplay.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/7a669e8218c18d407bc6b437871b7179.poster.avif?t=1699477566\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/7a669e8218c18d407bc6b437871b7179.webm?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/7a669e8218c18d407bc6b437871b7179.mp4?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Maps: Explore a variety of maps, each with its own environment and unique challenges.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/2c3bfda89d4aa3a373f317ae7745a604.poster.avif?t=1699477566\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/2c3bfda89d4aa3a373f317ae7745a604.webm?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/2c3bfda89d4aa3a373f317ae7745a604.mp4?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging Encounters: Confront a series of enemies on your journey, testing your skills and strategies.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/523b3bc366f56fa7339a88f056cdf315.poster.avif?t=1699477566\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/523b3bc366f56fa7339a88f056cdf315.webm?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602270/extras/523b3bc366f56fa7339a88f056cdf315.mp4?t=1699477566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
